Greetings! Here's a look at some of the things happening on Yahoo! in April:


New Features & Services


[IMAGE]

Yahoo! on Your Verizon Wireless Phone  - Stay informed wherever you go. Read

your email, check the markets, get news and sports scores, and stay ahead of

the weather -- all from Verizon's Mobile Web service.

[IMAGE]

Register a Personal Email Address  - Get the email address you've always

wanted and use it with your existing Yahoo! Mail account. Send and receive

email at an address that you create, such as me@my-own-name.com. This package

includes your own web domain and five unique mail accounts, all for only $35

per year.

[IMAGE]

File Your Taxes  - You can save time and effort by using online tax

preparation and filing services. Complete your return by answering a series

of easy questions, or have an H€Block professional review it for you. Looking

