Staying in Touch  - Faster than email, Yahoo! Messenger lets you send instant

messages to family, friends, and co-workers.  Communicate in real time from

your computer, PDA, pager, or cell phone. Try voice chat, play games, set up

alerts, and place phone calls over the Internet.

